{"article":{"id":360039701652,"url":"https://mackerelio.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/360039701652.json","html_url":"https://support.mackerel.io/hc/en-us/articles/360039701652-Is-it-possible-to-monitor-network-devices-","author_id":390085917472,"comments_disabled":true,"draft":false,"promoted":false,"position":0,"vote_sum":1,"vote_count":3,"section_id":360007911812,"created_at":"2020-02-24T08:05:30Z","updated_at":"2021-12-21T07:38:55Z","name":"Is it possible to monitor network devices?","title":"Is it possible to monitor network devices?","source_locale":"ja","locale":"en-us","outdated":false,"outdated_locales":[],"edited_at":"2021-03-24T06:45:10Z","user_segment_id":null,"permission_group_id":1305651,"content_tag_ids":[],"label_names":["ルーター","スイッチ","router","switch","snmp trap","ping","icmp"],"body":"\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eNetwork devices can be monitored through use of the following monitoring plugins.\u003cbr\u003e(Only compatible with Linux OS)\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003emackerel-plugin-snmp\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eRetrieve arbitrary MIB information with SNMP and post as a metric.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eSNMP Trap monitoring is not supported.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003echeck-ping\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eCheck ICMP communication and have alerts issued when interrupted.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ePlugins must be installed on and configured for a host installed with the mackerel-agent.\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eIt is not possible to monitor a network device by directly installing the mackerel-agent or plugin.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eSee \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://mackerel.io/docs/entry/overview#support-environments\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eSupported Environments\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003e for more details.\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eSee the help page and the plugin README linked below for more details regarding the installation and configuration of plugins.\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://mackerel.io/docs/entry/howto/mackerel-agent-plugins\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eUsing the official plugin pack to visualize middleware metrics - Mackerel Help\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://github.com/mackerelio/mackerel-agent-plugins/tree/master/mackerel-plugin-snmp\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003emackerel-agent-plugins/mackerel-plugin-snmp\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://github.com/mackerelio/go-check-plugins/tree/master/check-ping\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003ego-check-plugins/check-ping\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e"}}